The ceremonial garb of Waukeen's followers is shown here in characteristic form: gaudy, ornate, and overdone. A heavy, baroque cloak loaded with different precious metals worked into fine material in vibrant colors. The local high priest often carries a magical staff also decorated with precious metals and gems. Tristana serves the Kingdom of Cetha as Magistrate of Trade.
A well dressed human, Tucker returns your look with an easy smile.

The Kingdom's Magistrate and Commander of all of Cetha's Military forces is a tall, broad-shouldered man with a clean-cut beard. His salt-and-pepper hair falls about his ears, the only thing unkempt about him.
This suit of armor is magnificent.

This magic weapon has an unusual maker's mark. It is accompanied by a jeweled scabbard.
This magic shield has an unusual maker's mark.
A charming man in his early forties, the King of Cetha is popular and beloved of his people. He has dark hair and brilliant blue eyes that glimmer with intellect.

Its a well known fact that elves are foppish gits, barely able to lift their own swords without a limp-wristed floppy motion. It was for this very reason that these boots were forged. 

The master elven smith Yaldriirmathileh Mastiiramaeviil, spent many long hours making these boots for the elven protectors of the long forgotten court of Myth Drannor. When the kingdom fell, many of these boots were lost, some fell into the hands of those responsible for the fall, others are a prized possession from a dragons hoard. 

Perhaps the adventurer who has stumbled upon them now will use them to serve their intended purpose. Perhaps though, they have simply made another step along the road to obscurity.

The Secret Sash is actually a more noteworthy item due to it's secret stash  of various elicit substances.  Unkown to most, but enjoyed by a curious few, these rare leaves and powders are hidden within various small slits along the belt.  When ingested, the powerful herbs have a way of instilling a confident bliss in the user, aiding performers and entertainers with a euphoric ease.  Typically, Harpers have controlled the flow of these most enjoyable belts.
Created in great quantities by long forgotten mages, these weapons were apparently designed for sell or outfitting of armies.
Created in great quantities by long forgotten mages, these weapons were apparently designed for sell or outfitting of armies.
A woman in her late thirties. She is friendly, but seems to take her job quite seriously. Bouvier is the Minister of Recreation.

Value.value: *she smiles* Pleasant day, isn't it, darling? Pardon me, sweetheart. I'm doing some work right now.

value.0: An elderly woman tends to some of the mess in the ministry building.

Value.value: Sorry, I have much to do.
*rubs her hands together* Ah, my bones are acting up again...
